<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ de jiā nǐ de jiā zài nǎ lǐ? nǐ de qīn rén nǐ de qīn rén zài hé fāng?
 lù chéng yuǎn rèn wù zhòng, wǒ men kuài gǎn gōng. shí jiān dōu shì cōng cōng.
 wǒ men dōu lái duì zhǔ shuō zhěng jiù wǒ men de jiā. wǒ men dōu lái duì zhǔ shuō zhěng jiù wǒ men de jiā.
 zài yáo yuǎn de dōu shì lǐ zài yáo yuǎn de xiāng xià. qiú zhǔ zhěng jiù wǒ men de jiā.</lyrics>
<title>qiú zhǔ zhěng jiù wǒ men de jiā 迦南297</title>
